description: A token with a picture of a person with the word "Enke" imprinted on it.  You feel that this has a strange connection to some items.
A token with a picture of a person with the word "CritMedic" imprinted on it.  On the opposite side it says "Spiky Chitin Sword".
A token with a picture of a person with the word "Slax" imprinted on it.  On the opposite side it says "Bone Dagger; Spike Bat; Blade Bat; face rags".

A token with a picture of a group of people person with the word "Developers" imprinted on it.  You feel it has a strange connection to everything.  On the opposite side it says "Cataclysm: Dark Days Ahead" and "Thanks!" What the hell is Cataclysm: Dark Days Ahead?
